<subSubSection id="5FC46559FFF62E38FF3A2523744CFF05" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="210" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" type="discussion">
<paragraph id="176136D2FFF62E38FF3A2523744CFF05" blockId="8.[151,1437,865,2006]" lastBlockId="9.[151,1436,151,248]" lastPageId="9" lastPageNumber="210" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FF3A25237627F8DF" bold="true" box="[199,315,1801,1826]" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">Remarks.</emphasis>
The three specimens that were designated as “ 
<typeStatus id="C8658870FFF62E39FCA5252374A3F8DF" box="[856,959,1801,1826]" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">holotype</typeStatus>
, 
<typeStatus id="C8658870FFF62E39FC302520732CF8DF" box="[973,1072,1802,1826]" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">paratype</typeStatus>
, and 
<typeStatus id="C8658870FFF62E39FB8D252373D1F8DF" box="[1136,1229,1801,1826]" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">allotype</typeStatus>
” have their labels written as 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FEF32507758FF8BB" authority="Ghes., 1940" authorityName="Ghes." authorityYear="1940" box="[270,659,1837,1862]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalybaea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FEF3250776E3F8BB" box="[270,511,1837,1862]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">Ptilothyris chalybaea</emphasis>
Ghes., 1940
</taxonomicName>
. However, it was confirmed that Ghesquière himself, or possibly his technician, mislabeled “ 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FE51257B7572F897" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghesquiere. A" authorityYear="1940" box="[428,622,1873,1898]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="porphyrea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FE51257B753CF897" box="[428,544,1873,1898]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">porphyrea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
” as 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FD58257B747AF897" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghes." box="[677,870,1873,1898]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalybaea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FD58257B7404F897" box="[677,792,1873,1898]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">chalybaea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
, because all the data on the labels of 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FAD4257B77C4F873" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghes." class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalybaea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FAD4257B7280F897" box="[1321,1436,1873,1898]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">chalybaea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
are exactly written in the same way as those of 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FCFA255F74D9F873" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghesquiere. A" authorityYear="1940" box="[775,965,1909,1934]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="porphyrea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FCFA255F7467F873" box="[775,891,1909,1934]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">porphyrea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
in its description. Moreover, no name of 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FF6A25B37645F84F" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghes." box="[151,345,1945,1970]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalybaea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FF6A25B37616F84F" box="[151,266,1945,1970]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">chalybaea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
could be found in the NHMUK card index (Lepindex) or any other available references. Ghesquière (1940) probably described the species with a different name, 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FC342597739BF82B" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghesquiere. A" authorityYear="1940" box="[969,1159,1981,2006]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="porphyrea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FC3425977321F82B" box="[969,1085,1981,2006]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">porphyrea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
, instead of 
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF62E39FAFB25947280F82B" box="[1286,1436,1981,2006]" italics="true" pageId="8" pageNumber="209">
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF62E39FAFB25947284F82B" box="[1286,1432,1981,2006]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="8" pageNumber="209" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalybaea">P. chalybaea</taxonomicName>
,
</emphasis>
the one he originally suggested on the label under the specimen. In the Afromoths (2018), the name of 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF72E38FAF022B377C4FF28" authority="Ghes." authorityName="Ghesquiere. A" authorityYear="1940" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="210" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="porphyrea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF72E38FAF022B37280FF4D" box="[1293,1436,151,176]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="210">P. porphyrea</emphasis>
Ghes.
</taxonomicName>
has been used as the valid name, instead of 
<taxonomicName id="D0DE4D51FFF72E38FD2822977479FF28" box="[725,869,188,213]" class="Insecta" family="Lecithoceridae" genus="Ptilothyris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="9" pageNumber="210" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalybaea">
<emphasis id="25AAEAC0FFF72E38FD2822977479FF28" box="[725,869,188,213]" italics="true" pageId="9" pageNumber="210">P. chalybaea</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. After the publication of this revision, the correct labels with the valid name should be placed on the specimens.
</paragraph>
